Class PartialLRUEvictor

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.worker.block.BlockStoreEventListenerBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BlockStoreEventListener, Evictor

    public class PartialLRUEvictor
extends LRUEvictor
    This class is used to evict old blocks in certain StorageDir by LRU. The main difference between PartialLRU and LRU is that LRU choose old blocks among several StorageDirs until one StorageDir satisfies the request space, but PartialLRU select one StorageDir with maximum free space first and evict old blocks in the selected StorageDir by LRU
